{"tid":674710,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(漢賊不兩立) 烏克蘭間諜海豚遭俄國抓走   竟集體絕食而亡","createTime":"2018-05-23T03:02:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-23T13:10:27.000Z","uid":184679,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a382c5be066c6ee99d8b4e772a8423d1d484a3b6","tid":674710,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T03:02:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/UERoHJxmd7wGwDfsJIi8dg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/nownews.hk/292dd4ccc05827044cb7d23912c2378e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FUERoHJxmd7wGwDfsJIi8dg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fnownews.hk%2F292dd4ccc05827044cb7d23912c2378e&h=5d0387c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭過去曾訓練不少「軍事海豚」執行各種戰鬥任務。近日有烏克蘭官員表示， 2014 年克里米亞被俄國併吞後，曾接收一批「海豚軍隊」，原本俄國還想把牠們訓練成為俄國效命，但這群海豚超愛國，不僅拒絕聽命，甚至還「集體絕食致死」，烏克蘭官員大讚「連海豚都比人愛國」。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，自 70 年代開始，當時的蘇聯就展開訓練海豚的計畫，經訓練後的海豚可以辨識特殊的口哨聲，隨著潛水艦一同出海執行任務，例如放置炸彈、偵測水雷、攻擊敵方潛水部隊等等。 90 年代蘇聯解體後，這批軍事海豚就歸到烏克蘭軍方管轄。<br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭接收這批軍事海豚後仍持續培育海豚的計畫，直到 2014 年俄國併吞克里米亞，海豚的管轄權又回到了俄羅斯手上。不過近日一名烏克蘭官員巴賓（ Babin ）透露，這批海豚不但不聽從「侵略者」俄國人的命令，還集體絕食死亡。巴賓也表示，「相比之下，許多烏克蘭士兵的忠誠度還比海豚要來得小很多」<br />\n<br />\n不過，俄國政府否認巴賓的言論，認為他的說法都是「政治宣傳和謠言」。俄羅斯議員貝里克（ Dmitry Belik ）也說，所有的戰鬥海豚都在 2014 年被賣出或是自然死亡，並沒有所謂的「絕食行動」。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》則提到，海豚和狗有著類似的忠誠，也發生過被人類飼養的海豚，在伴侶死亡後絕食的相關案例。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%AF%94%E4%BA%BA%E9%82%84%E5%BF%A0%E8%AA%A0-%E7%83%8F%E5%85%8B%E8%98%AD%E9%96%93%E8%AB%9C%E6%B5%B7%E8%B1%9A%E9%81%AD%E4%BF%84%E5%9C%8B%E6%8A%93%E8%B5%B0-%E7%AB%9F%E9%9B%86%E9%AB%94%E7%B5%95%E9%A3%9F%E8%80%8C%E4%BA%A1-042750767.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%25AF%2594%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%2582%2584%25E5%25BF%25A0%25E8%25AA%25A0-%25E7%2583%258F%25E5%2585%258B%25E8%2598%25AD%25E9%2596%2593%25E8%25AB%259C%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E8%25B1%259A%25E9%2581%25AD%25E4%25BF%2584%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%258A%2593%25E8%25B5%25B0-%25E7%25AB%259F%25E9%259B%2586%25E9%25AB%2594%25E7%25B5%2595%25E9%25A3%259F%25E8%2580%258C%25E4%25BA%25A1-042750767.html&d=9hIK144lkxzBKkv7H8CMvRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=eef984b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%AF%94%E4%BA%BA%E9%82%84%E5%BF%A0%E8%AA%A0-%E7%83%8F%E5%85%8B%E8%98%AD%E9%96%93%E8%AB%9C%E6%B5%B7%E8%B1%9A%E9%81%AD%E4%BF%84%E5%9C%8B%E6%8A%93%E8%B5%B0-%E7%AB%9F%E9%9B%86%E9%AB%94%E7%B5%95%E9%A3%9F%E8%80%8C%E4%BA%A1-042750767.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77d1c031ea6aeef9761fd0b8229bb185f15e4848","tid":674710,"uid":54181,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T03:48:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"48aa9d902754da981917ff4544411c56bc739f94","tid":674710,"uid":34223,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"77d1c031ea6aeef9761fd0b8229bb185f15e4848","tid":674710,"uid":54181,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T03:48:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T05:03:34.000Z","msg":"蘇聯係烏賊 盟軍先係海豚"},{"pid":"c3eb25c7ae6bf4ac0471e5c56491ef6a4b2c52a5","tid":674710,"uid":63154,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T05:07:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/ifdZ3rNgK_c/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FifdZ3rNgK_c%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=786b9dd2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0a69dba0ca06b29c8829ca0653b0321797a5cd49","tid":674710,"uid":57376,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"48aa9d902754da981917ff4544411c56bc739f94","tid":674710,"uid":34223,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"77d1c031ea6aeef9761fd0b8229bb185f15e4848","tid":674710,"uid":54181,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T03:48:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"r